text: Hanke Gerdina Johannette Bruins Slot (born 20 October 1977) is a Dutch politician and military veteran who was the Minister of the Interior and Kingdom Relations from 2022 to 2023,"Utrechtse gedeputeerde Hanke Bruins Slot voorgedragen als nieuwe minister van Binnenlandse Zaken", Algemeen Dagblad (in Dutch), 2 January 2022. and as Minister of Foreign Affairs from 2023 until 2024.Stephanie van den Berg (4 September 2023), Dutch Interior Minister Bruins Slot set for foreign ministry Reuters. ==References== Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:Ministers of foreign affairs of the Netherlands Category:Members of the House of Representatives of the Netherlands Category:Dutch military people Category:Christian Democratic Appeal politicians Category:Politicians from Gelderland
title: Hanke Bruins Slot
